20:30.880 --> 20:32.188
OTIS!

20:32.300 --> 20:33.324
- I'M SO SORRY.
- WHAT DID YOU DO TO HIM?

20:33.430 --> 20:34.431
- THE WAIT AT THE VET
TOOK FOREVER.

20:34.540 --> 20:35.871
