WITH THIS.

20:35.990 --> 20:37.218
- WHY WOULD YOU--
- WHAT THE HELL HAPPENED?

20:37.330 --> 20:38.774
- HOW COULD YOU DO THIS?
- IT'S TWO STITCHES.

20:38.890 --> 20:40.221
