20:41.720 --> 20:42.926
- I'M SO SORRY.
[overlapping chatter]

20:43.030 --> 20:45.021
- MAX, HE'S GONNA BE OKAY.
HE'S GONNA BE OKAY.

20:45.140 --> 20:46.516
- I TOTALLY BLEW IT.
I'M SORRY.

20:46.620 --> 20:47.894
